UID:40q2vks4tf57iaahqmk8ejkllp@google.com
CREATED:20251209T175453Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special evening at the observatory as we explore 
 one of the most mesmerizing celestial events—a lunar eclipse! This Focus Ni
 ght will feature an engaging presentation about the upcoming eclipse\, incl
 uding what causes it\, what to look for\, and how to view it safely and enj
 oyably.<br><br><b>Please note: The actual lunar eclipse will take place sev
 eral hours later\, in the early morning hours\, so this event is designed t
 o prepare and excite you for what you'll see later that night. While we won
 ’t observe the eclipse live during the program\, you’ll leave with everythi
 ng you need to appreciate it when it happens.</b><br><br>Our knowledgeable 
 docents will guide you through the science of eclipses\, share tips for vie
 wing\, and offer telescope views of other celestial objects visible that ev
 ening.<br><br>What to Expect:<br><br>• A focused presentation on the upcomi
 ng lunar eclipse<br><br>• Tips for viewing the eclipse in the early morning
 <br><br>• Telescope viewing of planets\, stars\, and deep-sky objects<br><b
 r>• Night-sky tours and Q&amp\;A with observatory docents<br><br>Don’t miss
  this chance to deepen your understanding of this celestial event before wi
 tnessing it for yourself.<br><br>The program starts promptly at 7:00 PM. Pl
 ease allow ample time for driving and parking. Sales are limited to 40 gues
 ts so we can provide a more personal experience. You'll have plenty of time
  at the telescope eyepieces\, and as always\, the observatory will be staff
 ed by knowledgeable and enthusiastic volunteers eager to show you the night
  sights\, and answer any questions you may have.<br><br>$50.00 per adult\, 
 $45.00 for seniors (62+) and students\, and $40 for members. Cost includes 
 the Sugarloaf Ridge State Park parking fee.<br><br>You MUST have a ticket t
 o attend this event.  Attendance is limited. Please note that tickets are n
 on-refundable and cannot be used for future events. Purchase tickets at <a 
 href="http://rfo.simpletix.com">rfo.simpletix.com</a>.
LAST-MODIFIED:20251219T230735Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Focus Night: Lunar Eclipse
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
