UID:7i6bb5tq0dkc7avovs14vtop5t@google.com
CREATED:20221104T042812Z
DESCRIPTION:Thank you for supporting the observatory! Please join us for an
  informal open house. Come for a tour\, meet docents\,  and check out our t
 elescopes! \n\nDrive past the Sugarloaf Ridge park entry kiosk and park in 
 the lot by the white barn.\n\nDo dress warmly\; telescope rooms are open to
  the night air and it gets cold.\n\nRed lights only at the observatory to p
 rotect night vision\; bring a red flashlight if you have one — or we'll giv
 e you some red cellophane to cover your white flashlight.\n\nWhile this eve
 nt is free to members and docents and their families\, please sign up at rf
 o.simpletix.com using your member code so we know how many people to expect
 . Thank you!\n\nIf there are additional questions\, please email info@rfo.o
 rg. Thank you\, and we look forward to seeing you at future events. 
LAST-MODIFIED:20221221T195723Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Docent and Member Night
