 (Plus State Park Parking Fee $10.00 per vehicle.)&nbsp\;Please note\, proof
  of Covid vaccination or a negative Covid test within the last 48 hours req
 uired.</html-blob><br><html-blob><br></html-blob><br><html-blob>Our July pu
 blic star party will also have some special activities to celebrate NASA's 
 first science-quality images from the James Webb Space Telescope being rele
 ased on July 12th (you can see it webcast live at Space.com along with NASA
 's website and social media channels). To celebrate this momentous occasion
 \, we’ll be having a special guest speaker\, Tom Scheffelin\, at our July p
 ublic star party\, and will have some other special activities that night a
 s well. Tom is a NASA Solar System Ambassador\, a Scouts BSA STEM volunteer
 \, and a SPIE volunteer.&nbsp\;<br></html-blob>
