CREATED:20200906T182026Z
DESCRIPTION:If you’ve ever looked up at the stars overhead and wondered wha
 t else is up there\, the Robert Ferguson Observatory’s “Whats Up?” program 
 is designed for you! The event will feature a talk on objects in our local 
 galaxy\, the Milky Way\, and very deep space objects beyond\, plus you will
  get plenty of time at the telescope eyepieces. Tickets may be purchased vi
 a Brown Paper Tickets. 
LAST-MODIFIED:20200906T182713Z
