CREATED:20250924T185448Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Ice-cream sundaes\, hot chocolate\, and a field full of tele
 scopes. What more could a stargazer ask for? For this special summer gather
 ing\, we invite members and volunteers to bring their own telescopes of any
  size or condition. Brand new? Perfect. A little dusty? Even better. Not wo
 rking at all? Bring it anyway! Our volunteers will be ready to help diagnos
 e\, align\, and point it toward the wonders of the night sky.</p><p><br>We’
 ll start the evening at our out-of-this-world Ice Cream Sundae Station\, wh
 ere you can build the perfect summer treat before settling in for a short p
 resentation on telescope types and essential components.</p><p><br>Afterwar
 d\, we’ll warm up with hot chocolate and tea\, then head outside to explore
  the cosmos together through your telescopes and ours.</p><p><br>Please Not
 e: This event is for our members and volunteers only. While admission is fr
 ee\, please sign up in advance so we know how many guests to expect. Thank 
 you!</p><p>Not yet a member? Join here:<a href="https://rfo.org/index.php/m
 embership/">https://rfo.org/index.php/membership/</a></p><p>For additional 
 questions\, please email info@rfo.org. We look forward to seeing you at fut
 ure events!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260112T180215Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Scoops & Scopes ~ Docent and Member Party!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
