DESCRIPTION:Thank you for supporting the observatory! Please join us for an
  informal open house. Come for a tour\, meet docents\,  and check out our t
 elescopes! \n\nDrive past the Sugarloaf Ridge park entry kiosk and park in 
 the lot by the white barn.\n\nDo dress warmly\; telescope rooms are open to
  the night air and it gets cold.\n\nRed lights only at the observatory to p
 rotect night vision\; bring a red flashlight if you have one — or we&#39\;l
 l give you some red cellophane to cover your white flashlight.\n\nWhile thi
 s event is free to members and docents and their families\, please sign up 
 at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://rfo.simpletix.com&amp\;sa=D
 &amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1702171659297715&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3L7h_MItQa5j
 li1FTiv5sJ" target="_blank">rfo.simpletix.com</a> using your member code so
  we know how many people to expect. Thank you!\n\nIf there are additional q
 uestions\, please email <a href="mailto:info@rfo.org" target="_blank">info@
 rfo.org</a>. Thank you\, and we look forward to seeing you at future events
 . 
