DESCRIPTION:Thank you for supporting the observatory! Please join us for an
  informal open house. Come for a tour\, meet docents\,  and check out our t
 elescopes! And of course\, enjoy some hot spiced cider or hard cider\, swee
 t treats\, and some fun harvest/autumn activities!\n\nDrive past the Sugarl
 oaf Ridge park entry kiosk and park in the lot by the white barn.\n\nDo dre
 ss warmly\; telescope rooms are open to the night air and it gets cold.\n\n
 Red lights only at the observatory to protect night vision\; bring a red fl
 ashlight if you have one — or we'll give you some red cellophane to cover y
 our white flashlight.\n\nWhile this event is free to members and docents an
 d their families\, please sign up at rfo.simpletix.com using your member co
 de so we know how many people to expect. Thank you!\n\nNot a member? You ca
 n sign up for membership here: https://rfo.org/index.php/membership/\n\nIf 
 there are additional questions\, please email info@rfo.org. Thank you\, and
  we look forward to seeing you at future events.
