DESCRIPTION:MARS… the red planet. This rocky planet\, fourth from the Sun\,
  could harbor life and is the focus of much science and intrigue. Come lear
 n what makes this planet so interesting and discover the autumn sky.<br><br
 >Please visit <a href="https://www.brownpapertickets.com/event/4813417" id=
 "ow323" __is_owner="true">Brown Paper Tickets</a>&nbsp\;for important infor
 mation and to buy tickets. Seating is limited and you MUST have a ticket to
  attend this event\; tickets will not be sold at the door.<br><br>Cost is $
 25 per adult ($20 for seniors or under 18) and includes the State Park park
 ing fee.
