CREATED:20250924T185937Z
DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">Our family day programs are created specifically f
 or families with children 12 and under. Young explorers will discover the w
 onders of our solar system through hands-on activities\, interactive learni
 ng\, and plenty of outdoor excitement! </p><br>Advanced tickets are require
 d. Purchase tickets at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com" target="_blank">r
 fo.simpletix.com</a>. There must be at least one adult chaperone per family
