DESCRIPTION:<u></u><p>Do you have a telescope at home that you just don’t u
 se because you’re not sure how it works? Or\, are you looking to purchase o
 r upgrade a telescope but don’t know where to start? Then this class is for
  you! You will work on-one-one with our knowledgeable docents who will guid
 e you in collimating and operating your telescope\, and the basics of teles
 cope operations. Please email Stephanie at <a href="mailto:sd@rfo.org" targ
 et="_blank">sd@rfo.org</a> to inform her what type of scope you are bringin
 g prior to the event so we can be best prepared to help you.  </p><p>You MU
 ST have a ticket to attend this event\; tickets will not be sold at the doo
 r. Purchase tickets at: <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com" target="_blank">
 rfo.simpletix.com</a> </p><p> </p><u></u>
