DESCRIPTION:<p>Presentations on astronomical topics are given in the classr
 oom throughout the course of the evening. Starting at dusk\, the Observator
 y’s three main telescopes are open for your viewing. Docents set up additio
 nal telescopes in front of the building. Friendly and knowledgeable docents
  are available to answer your questions. $10.00 per adult\, $5.00 per stude
 nt\, youth\, and seniors 60+\, under 12 FREE. (Plus State Park Parking Fee 
 $10.00 per vehicle.) Purchase tickets at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com"
 >rfo.simpletix.com</a>.&nbsp\;</p>
