 scopes. Guests will be in small groups with individual RFO docents and trea
 ted to an hour long laser guided tour of the constellations.&nbsp\;</p><p>P
 lease visit <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com">rfo.simpletix.com</a> for im
 portant information and to buy tickets. You MUST have a ticket to attend th
 is event\; tickets will not be sold at the door.</p><p>$10.00 per adult\, $
 5.00 per student\, and under 12 FREE.</p><p>(Plus State Park Parking Fee $1
 0.00 per vehicle.)</p>
