DESCRIPTION:<p>Bring Your Own Binoculars and Chair! This is a guided tour i
 nto the wonders of the night sky that are visible through common binoculars
 . Guests will station their chairs in the parking lot outside the observato
 ry and knowledgeable docents with laser pointers will guide guests to the h
 idden secrets of the night sky. Expect to see double stars\, open star clus
 ters\, globular clusters\, maybe even a planet or two!<br><br>Please visit 
 <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://rfo.simpletix.com&amp\;sa=D&a
 mp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1759171003342407&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3EyfQ9iFOS_Kcc
 4QmBpsoM" target="_blank">https://rfo.simpletix.com</a> for important infor
 mation and to buy tickets. You MUST have a ticket to attend this event\; ti
 ckets will not be sold at the door. <strong>Please note that tickets are no
 n-refundable and cannot be used for future events. </strong></p><p>Cost is 
 $35 per adult ($30 for seniors or under 18) and includes the State Park par
 king fee.</p><p> </p>
