  throughout the course of the evening. Starting at dusk\, the Observatory’s
  three main telescopes are open for your viewing. Docents set up additional
  telescopes in front of the building. Friendly and knowledgeable docents ar
 e available to answer your questions. $5.00 per adult\, under 18 FREE.(Plus
  State Park Parking Fee $10.00 per vehicle.)
