DESCRIPTION:<p>Bring your Valentine to our Bring Your Own Binoculars and Ch
 air night! This is a guided tour into the wonders of the night sky that are
  visible through common binoculars. Guests will station their chairs in the
  parking lot outside the observatory and knowledgeable docents with laser p
 ointers will guide guests to the hidden secrets of the night sky. Expect to
  see double stars\, open star clusters\, globular clusters\, maybe even a p
 lanet or two!<br><br>Please visit <a href="https://rfo.simpletix.com" targe
 t="_blank">https://rfo.simpletix.com</a> for important information and to b
 uy tickets. You MUST have a ticket to attend this event\; tickets will not 
 be sold at the door. <strong>Please note that tickets are non-refundable an
 d cannot be used for future events. </strong></p><p>Cost is $35 per adult (
 $30 for seniors or under 18) and includes the State Park parking fee.</p><p
