DESCRIPTION:<u></u><u></u><u></u>Have you ever wondered what&#39\;s really 
 out there in the night sky? Wished you could zoom in on cosmic marvels? Wha
 t if you had a handful of astronomers at your elbow\, showing the way\, ans
 wering your questions in plain language? That&#39\;s a Focus Night at the R
 obert Ferguson Observatory! These are small groups so you get plenty of sco
 pe time\, and a chance to focus on Jupiter\, the largest planet in our sola
 r system! Learn about the Great Red Spot\, the four Galilean moons\, missio
 ns to Jupiter\, and much more.<br> <br>If you&#39\;ve never seen Jupiter in
  a telescope\, you&#39\;re missing out on the thrill of a lifetime. But tha
 t&#39\;s not all! Other spectacles of the night sky\, including nebulae and
  galaxies\, also await.<br> <br>The program starts promptly at 7:00 PM. Aft
 erward\, weather permitting\, we will move to two of  RFO&#39\;s telescopes
  (an 8&quot\; refractor and a 40&quot\; reflector) for a deeper exploration
 . Sales are limited to 40 guests so we can provide a more personal experien
 ce. You&#39\;ll have plenty of time at the telescope eyepieces\, and as alw
 ays\, the observatory will be staffed by knowledgeable and enthusiastic vol
 unteers eager to show you the night sights\, and answer any questions you m
 ay have.<br><br>The program begins promptly at 7:00 pm. Allow generous time
  to arrive and park.<br><br>$50.00 per adult\, $45.00 for seniors (62+) and
  students\, and $40 for members. Cost includes the Sugarloaf Ridge State Pa
 rk parking fee.<br> <br>You MUST have a ticket to attend this event.  Atten
 dance is limited. Please note that tickets are non-refundable and cannot be
  used for future events. <br><br>RFO is operated by the Valley of the Moon 
 Observatory Association\, a 501(3)(c) nonprofit organization\, and all of t
 he proceeds will go towards maintaining this beloved Sonoma county institut
 ion.<br><u></u><br>Please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http:
 //www.rfo.simpletix.com&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=17297140896
 32601&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1GEULFTH7YXYc9-l9ngLav" target="_blank">www.rfo.simple
 tix.com</a> for important information and to buy tickets. Seating is limite
 d and you MUST have a ticket to attend this event\; tickets will not be sol
 d at the door.<br><br><br><u></u><u></u><u></u>
