CREATED:20251125T231409Z
DESCRIPTION:Sips and Stars ~ an evening of fine wine and cosmic wonder.<br>
 <br>Join us for a magical night under the stars at the Robert Ferguson Obse
 rvatory! Our Sips &amp\; Stars event blends the beauty of the night sky wit
 h the elegance of Sonoma County wine. Enjoy a curated tasting experience ho
 sted by Landmark Vineyards\, known for their exceptional Chardonnay and Pin
 ot Noir\, while taking in breathtaking views of the cosmos through our powe
 rful telescopes.<br><br>As twilight falls\, relax with a glass of wine in h
 and and listen to engaging astronomy talks from our knowledgeable docents. 
 Once darkness settles\, step up to the observatory’s telescopes for guided 
 viewing of planets\, star clusters\, and distant galaxies.<br><br>Whether y
 ou’re a wine lover\, stargazer\, or simply looking for a unique evening out
  in Sonoma Valley\, Sips &amp\; Stars promises an unforgettable experience 
 where earthly pleasures meet celestial beauty.<br><br>Guests must be 21 or 
 older to attend and each registration includes two drink tickets. Proceeds 
 support the Robert Ferguson Observatory’s public education programs.<br><br
 >Space is limited - register at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com">rfo.simp
 letix.com</a>
