DESCRIPTION:The RFO is a place where individual volunteers make a differenc
 e: it’s a place where ideas come to life. The Observatory was built and is 
 maintained by volunteers. All of the public events\, private events\, class
 es\, and labs were conceived by and brought to fruition by volunteers. RFO’
 s volunteers work together\, combining skills and talents to create this sp
 ecial place. Interested in volunteering? Fill out an application.<br><br>(P
 lease sign up in advance)<br><h3><b><strong><b><a href="https://app.betteri
 mpact.com/Application?OrganizationGuid=178bfcf5-d9de-498d-991f-3ae5c3b5ce18
 "><u>Volunteer Application Form</u></a></b></strong></b></h3>
