DESCRIPTION:Interested in volunteering for RFO? Sign up for this 3-week vir
 tual training to learn the ins and outs of becoming involved with the obser
 vatory! Hands-on telescope training will follow once we are able to safely 
 open the facility to the public. However\, completing this virtual training
  will allow you to volunteer for our outdoor events and become involved in 
 other activities for the organization. Please note that you must be able to
  attend all three trainings on 3/4\, 3/11\, and 3/18. Fill out an applicati
 on here: https://rfo.org/index.php/volunteer/
