DESCRIPTION:<p>Thank you for supporting the observatory! Please join us for
  an informal open house. Come for a tour\, meet docents\, &nbsp\;and check 
 out our telescopes!&nbsp\;</p><p>Drive past the Sugarloaf Ridge park entry 
 kiosk and park in the lot by the white barn.</p><p>Do dress warmly\; telesc
 ope rooms are open to the night air and it gets cold.</p><p>Red lights only
  at the observatory to protect night vision\; bring a red flashlight if you
  have one — or we'll give you some red cellophane to cover your white flash
 light.</p><p>While this event is free to members and docents and their fami
 lies\, please sign up at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com">rfo.simpletix.c
 om</a>&nbsp\;using your member code&nbsp\;so we know how many people to exp
 ect. Thank you!</p><p>If there are additional questions\, please email info
 @rfo.org. Thank you\, and we look forward to seeing you at future events.&n
 bsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220815T174526Z
