CREATED:20260112T175813Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Put your space knowledge to the test in an evening of astron
 omy-themed fun! From celestial phenomena to rockets\, satellites\, and icon
 ic sci-fi\, our three-round trivia game will challenge beginners and season
 ed stargazers alike. Prizes will be awarded for 1st\, 2nd\, and 3rd place\,
  and even if you don’t take home a win\, you’ll still enjoy an assortment o
 f sweet treats and astronomical delights throughout the night.</p><p>After 
 trivia concludes\, we’ll open our three telescopes for a guided observing s
 ession under the night sky.</p><p>Trivia teams may include up to five parti
 cipants\, and we encourage mixing groups to meet new people. Plus\, our vol
 unteers tend to be very useful when astronomy questions arise.<br> </p><p>W
 hile this event is free to members and docents and their families\, please 
 sign up at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com" target="_blank"><u>rfo.simple
 tix.com</u></a> using your member code so we know how many people to expect
 . Thank you!</p><p>Not a member? You can sign up for membership here: <a hr
 ef="https://rfo.org/index.php/membership/" target="_blank"><u>https://rfo.o
 rg/index.php/membership/</u></a><br></p><p>If there are additional question
 s\, please email info@rfo.org. Thank you\, and we look forward to seeing yo
 u at future events. </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260112T181026Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Treats and Trivia ~ Docent and Member Party!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
