DESCRIPTION:<p>Bring Your Own Binoculars and Chair! This is a guided tour i
 nto the wonders of the night sky that are visible through common binoculars
 . Guests will station their chairs at socially distanced locations in the p
 arking lot outside the observatory and knowledgeable docents with laser poi
 nters will guide guests to the hidden secrets of the night sky. Expect to s
 ee double stars\, open star clusters\, globular clusters\, maybe even a pla
 net or two!<br><br>Please visit https://rfo.simpletix.com&nbsp\;for importa
 nt information and to buy tickets. You MUST have a ticket to attend this ev
 ent\; tickets will not be sold at the door.<br><br>Cost is $25 per adult ($
 20 for seniors or under 18) and includes the State Park parking fee.</p><p>
 &nbsp\;</p>
