CREATED:20221202T194547Z
DESCRIPTION:Zero to Hero: A Backyard Astronomer’s Adventure! This 6-session
  series will guide beginning astronomers into how to become better backyard
  astronomers. No equipment will be necessary. The class will explore where 
 to start\, how to decide what telescope to purchase\, problem solving\, and
  more! We look forward to helping you set and reach your astronomy goals wh
 ile you expand your knowledge\, from the beauty of the night sky to the equ
 ipment used to observe it. For more information and to purchase tickets ple
 ase visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://rfo.simpletix.com&am
 p\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1670442321969070&amp\;usg=AOvVaw39xIz
 uc1amCSKxRHpI0cxB" target="_blank">rfo.simpletix.com</a><span>. </span>
