CREATED:20201228T224721Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>This event has been cancelled due to COVID-19 stay-at-home o
 rders.</p><p>Bring Your Own Binoculars and Chair! This is a guided tour int
 o the wonders of the night sky that are visible through common binoculars. 
 Guests will station their chairs at socially distanced locations in the par
 king lot outside the observatory and knowledgeable docents with laser point
 ers will guide guests to the hidden secrets of the night sky. Expect to see
  double stars\, open star clusters\, globular clusters and Mars!<br><br>Ple
 ase visit Brown Paper Tickets (link coming soon) for important information 
 and to buy tickets. You MUST have a ticket to attend this event\; tickets w
 ill not be sold at the door.<br><br>Cost is $25 per adult ($20 for seniors 
 or under 18) and includes the State Park parking fee.</p><p>&nbsp\;</p>
