 ng-you-need-to-know-perseid-meteor-shower/">Perseids Meteor Shower</a> peak
 s this week\, but due to the recent COVID developments\, RFO will not be op
 ening for a Perseids Event.&nbsp\; There may be some RFO docents choosing t
 o view the Perseids from the RFO parking lot who usually aren’t shy about t
 alking about and sharing their knowledge of the night sky.&nbsp\; If you co
 me up\, plan to bring a chair or blanket\, relax\, and look to the sky in s
 earch of&nbsp\;meteors.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
