DESCRIPTION:MARS… the red planet. This rocky planet\, fourth from the Sun\,
  could harbor life and is the focus of much science and intrigue. Come lear
 n what makes this planet so interesting and discover the autumn sky.\n\n\nO
 n this date Mars will be at its very best and will be at a good altitude fo
 r the relatively rare Mars opposition (when it will be closest to earth).\n
 \nPlease visit www.rfo.simpletix.com for important information and to buy t
 ickets. Seating is limited and you MUST have a ticket to attend this event\
 ; tickets will not be sold at the door.\n\nCost is $50 per adult\, $40 for 
 members\, and $45 for seniors or under 18 students and includes the State P
 ark parking fee.
