LOCATION:Robert Ferguson Observatory\, 2605 Adobe Canyon Rd\, Kenwood\, CA 
 95452\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Focus Night: Mars
TRANSP:OPAQUE
