UID:05oo1kaqa49oqho5mp7v2sgutk@google.com
CREATED:20241024T154918Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for Cosmic Conversations\, a special interactive eve
 ning of exploration and discovery at the Robert Ferguson Observatory! This 
 unique event offers an intimate\, small-group experience\, ensuring plenty 
 of time for questions and in-depth discussions about the observatory and fa
 scinating astronomical topics.</p><p>Your night begins with an exclusive be
 hind-the-scenes tour of our observatory\, where you’ll get an insider’s loo
 k at our telescopes and instruments and learn how we unlock the mysteries o
 f the cosmos. Then\, join our expert astronomers for a guided Q&amp\;A sess
 ion\, where no question is too big or too small. We’ll have a variety of to
 pics prepared for discussion and we encourage you to bring questions of you
 r own. Cosmic questions are not required for entry but now’s your chance to
  ask anything about black holes\, distant galaxies\, or the origins of our 
 universe. Whether you're a seasoned stargazer or just curious about the cos
 mos\, this event is perfect for all ages and experience levels. Our knowled
 geable astronomers will do their best to answer your queries about the nigh
 t sky\, space exploration\, and everything in between. </p><p>As the night 
 deepens\, step up to our telescopes to view distant galaxies\, nebulae\, pl
 anets\, and other celestial wonders. Finally\, to keep you warm while you s
 targaze\, we’ll be serving complimentary tea and hot cocoa.</p><p>Whether y
 ou’re a lifelong astronomy enthusiast or just beginning your cosmic journey
 \, Cosmic Conversations promises a night of wonder\, learning\, and unforge
 ttable views of the universe! Bring your curiosity\, and we’ll provide the 
 universe!<br></p><p>Purchase tickets at <a href="http://rfo.simpletix.com" 
 target="_blank">rfo.simpletix.com</a>. </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250329T175522Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Cosmic Conversations
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
