DESCRIPTION:<p>Jupiter...the fifth planet from the Sun and the largest in t
 he Solar System. This gas giant has a mass one-thousandth that of the Sun\,
  but two-and-a-half times that of all the other planets in the Solar System
  combined. Come learn about this fascinating planetary system and discover 
 the autumn sky. (Ticket link coming soon!)</p>
